notes.title: Today was my first day at Finix!
notes.details: So far it's going ok. I continue to give cringe answers about myself, but what else is new. I can't wait to actually get my hands dirty. I'm praying I'll be able to pick things up quickly and add value to the team. Otherwise I'm just this workout asshole who is in way over my head. I can't allow that. I've got way to much riding on this. Sad face emoji goes here.

notes.title: Thanks Net Ninja
notes.details: Net ninja always gives great tutorials. I've been putting of learning material UI, but no more! Thanks to the ninja, I feel I have a firm grasp on this. As always, AWESOME!
